@startuml 16.1_createCommentBlog
hide footbox
actor User as "Users"
boundary PostPage as View
control "CommentPostController" as Controller
participant ":CommentPostService" as Service
participant ":CommentPostModel" as Model
database Database as Database


User -> View : 1. Input comment content
activate View
activate User
View -> View : 2. Validate input
activate View
deactivate View

opt Invalid Input or fields left empty
    View --> User : 2.1. Show validation error
end

    View -> Controller : 3. Create comment request
    activate Controller

    Controller -> Service : 4. createComment(commentData)
    activate Service
        Service -> Model : 5. save(commentData)
        activate Model

        Model -> Database : 6. Execute insert query
        activate Database
        Database --> Model : 7. Return result
        deactivate Database

        Model --> Service : 8. Return created entity
        deactivate Model

alt Create comment successful
        Service --> Controller : 8.1. Return CommentPostResponse
        Controller --> View : 8.1.1. Return response
        View --> User : 8.1.2. Redirect to post page with new comment
else Create comment failed
        Service --> Controller : 8.2. Return error
        deactivate Service
        Controller --> View : 8.2.1. Return error response
        deactivate Controller
        View --> User : 8.2.2. Display error message
        deactivate View
        deactivate User
end
@enduml
